data.description: Experience the best of North Port living in this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, where comfort and convenience harmonize seamlessly. With a two car garage and a generous yard, this home offers a welcoming retreat. Discover the thoughtfully curated finishes and decorative touches that add character to each space.Embrace the coastal lifestyle with beautiful beaches just a short distance away. Enjoy shopping and dining in nearby Downtown Wellen Park. More than just a house, this home embodies a cozy haven, providing a perfect blend of warmth and accessibility in Sarasota County. Welcome to your new sanctuary.
